  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/976010/extras/765d82aa0bc827b0a1a2c50a2cd49bf0.avif?t=1743090511\" width=620 height=200 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Each level is a new mechanic. It will be funny!<br></li><li>More than a hundred levels. 100 ordinary, 10 extra complex and 10 secret!<br></li><li>Use the environment. Everything you see on the screen can help you get through, even an interface or a mouse!<br></li><li>Retro atmosphere. Stylish pixel art graphics in two colors that can be customized!<br>Fresh Chiptune / 8bit Soundtrack by HateBit!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/976010/extras/b0718d678db5f639ef08c4b3500f16c1.avif?t=1743090511\" width=620 height=200 /></span><br>The main character like the last idiot got on a clickbait and downloaded \"the best game ever\". Mysteriously, he got inside the computer and to get out, he has to solve all the puzzles and just survive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/976010/extras/2cbeb53f8850290ecdcebb649e6caf4c.avif?t=1743090511\" width=620 height=200 /></span><br>Game developed <strong>Pixel Error</strong><br>Music by <strong>HateBit</strong><br>Intro comics - <strong>Oblom studio</strong>",
